== 家庭 ==
2004年7月25日，孟庭葦與高中同學張志鵬結婚，婚宴於兩人當時就讀的南投縣南投市[[國立中興高級中學|國立中興高級中學]]舉辦。

2007年2月18日，兒子張彧出生，綽號小寶弟<ref>{{cite news|title=孟庭葦：兒子是南印度高僧轉世 佛緣跡象明顯|url=http://www.renminbao.info/122/6117.htm|newspaper=[[人民報|人民報]]|date=|language=zh|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131230937/http://www.renminbao.info/122/6117.htm|archivedate=2015-01-31|accessdate=2015-01-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=44歲孟庭葦兒子近照曝光 |url=http://www.mmready.com/content/124094.html |newspaper=[[媽咪學堂|媽咪學堂]] |date=2014-08-19 |language=zh-tw |access-date=2015-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201001227/http://www.mmready.com/content/124094.html |archive-date=2015-02-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2014年7月25日，孟庭葦在微博發表離婚聲明，稱自己和張志鵬已在2013年1月簽字離婚<ref>{{cite news |title = 傳孟庭葦離婚 老公張志鵬否認 承認會吵架 |url = http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/23/a1124820.html |publisher = [[新唐人電視臺|新唐人電視臺]] |date = 2014-07-22 |language = zh |access-date = 2015-01-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201001339/http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/23/a1124820.html |archive-date = 2015-02-01 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 老公要紀念結婚十年 孟庭葦稱早已離婚 |url = http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/25/a1125427.html |publisher = [[新唐人電視臺|新唐人電視臺]] |date = 2014-07-25 |language = zh |access-date = 2015-01-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201001301/http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2014/07/25/a1125427.html |archive-date = 2015-02-01 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = 孟庭苇和母亲儿子庆生 前夫送祝福 |url = http://yule.sohu.com/20141222/n407178218.shtml |publisher = [[搜狐|搜狐]] |date = 2014-12-22 |language = zh-cn |access-date = 2015-01-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201001214/http://yule.sohu.com/20141222/n407178218.shtml |archive-date = 2015-02-01 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2018年11月，前夫张志鹏在微博爆料两人离婚原因是因为孟婚内出轨同性女助理。孟庭苇否认，孟庭苇工作室微博和脸书提供了多项实际证据证明孟庭苇多年来遭受前夫索要钱财，前夫威胁孟不提供就进行污蔑等实际对话记录证据<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://weibo.com/5971121165/H42fdaOod |title=孟庭苇工作室微博 |access-date=2022-01-10 |archive-date=2022-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110213708/https://weibo.com/5971121165/H42fdaOod }}</ref>。

